{"type":null,"faqId":16791,"title":"Mate7锁屏状态下，微信无法收到消息怎么办？","answer":"<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\"></p>\n<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\">您好，请确认以下几点设置：</p>\n<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\">1、打开微信的通知开关，进入微信-菜单“我”-设置-新消息提醒-打开开关</p>\n<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\">2、打开系统的微信通知，设置-应用程序管理-微信-显示通知</p>\n<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\">3、将微信添加到“受保护的后台应用”，全部设置-隐私和安全(更多)-受保护的后台应用-微信，打开开关</p>\n<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\">4、始终保护数据连接，设置-无线和网络(更多)-移动网络-始终连接数据业务--勾选</p>\n<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\">5、设置，WLAN，高级设置，在休眠状态下操持WLAN连接，选择始终</p>\n<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\">6、设置，省电管理，设置为普通省电（智能省电无操作熄屏30分钟后自动关闭后台应用）</p>\n<br>\n<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\"></p>","faqTypeId":139,"faqType":"应用程序管理","useful":6,"unUseful":9,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9435","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Application-Management","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1417250414000,"seriesProductName":"Jazz-CL00,Jazz-TL00,Jazz-TL10,Jazz-UL00","visitedTimes":1852,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":8,"times":2,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"2","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"Mate7，Jazz-CL00,Jazz-TL00,Jazz-TL10,Jazz-UL00,锁屏,微信消息,锁屏微信","avgScore":4.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}